I only vaguely knew who Kobe was, but hearing about what happened, and watching glimpses of his life and spirit through various clips really tore my heart.

Learning that his daughter was also on that flight brought an almost unbearable feeling of grief and sadness. I watched and cried in disbelief, only imagining how his friends and family are feeling at that moment.


I’m just a stranger, but I share their pain.
